title: The Artie Lange Show - Complete Archive - 2013/2014
description:
The Artie Lange Show (2013-2014)

Credits and thanks to Wush, Bonehead, Baba Booeys Tooth, Milkweed, Flykev, chaser469 and @falatoradio for sharing shows making it possible for me to create this archive.

Take care, brush your hair!

Show your support by following Artie & Mike Bocchetti on twitter @artiequitter & @MIKEBOCCHETTI or go to http://artiequitter.com/ & http://www.mikebocchetti.com/

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The Artie Lange Show was a syndicated sports/entertainment talk show hosted by comedian and former Howard Stern Show personality Artie Lange. The show was originally launched in 2011 as The Nick & Artie Show, with Lange as co-host to Nick DiPaolo;DiPaolo left the show in January of 2013, with Lange citing creative differences between DiPaolo and DirecTV. It is currently produced by DirecTV Sports Group and is syndicated by Premiere Radio Networks. The three-hour program broadcasts live Monday - Friday beginning 10 pm ET/ 7 pm PT on radio. DirecTV airs the show on The Audience Network Tuesday - Friday from 2 am - 5 am ET and live Friday from 10 pm ET to 1 am ET Saturday.

Along with being broadcast on the radio, the show is also available to stream live 24/7 and download from artielangeshow.com. The show is also available as a podcast from iTunes and as a mobile app from Stitcher Radio.

On September 7, 2012, the show began broadcasting on DirecTV's Audience Network.

The show was cancelled in April 2014; Lange announced the cancellation on the final show on April 28.
